    "Event.Railroad_start-s2": "No, not really.",
    "Event.Railroad_talk": "I'm waiting for a train to pass by$0.#$b#They don't show up often, but the wait is worth it.$0#$b#Like birdwatching, but with trains.",
    "Event.Railroad_mid-a1": "Have you seen any so far?",
