    "Event.Railroad_mid-s1": "Two, up until now.$0#$b#The last train was full of coal, and some bits dropped as it passed by...$2#$b#So I hope to see the train better next time.",
    "Event.Railroad_mid-s2": "These machines are amazing. Did you know? They can run on 4 types of energy: Horse-pulled, Steam, Diesel, and Electricity.$1#$b#I used to live in a location where you could only get by train.$0",
    "Event.Railroad_mid-s3": "Well, what's the point in farming?$5",
    "Event.Railroad_end": "...At any rate, you can stay if you want.$0#$b#But i'm warning you, something may fall when the train comes.$0#$e#I hope you have something to cover yourself with.$1",
    
    //  event: Forest
    "Event.Forest_1": "Hey, @.",
    "Event.Forest_2": "You know, i used to be a teacher there- at the town where i grew in. $0#$b#We were far from the big city, and sustained ourselves by farming.$0#$b#...Then things changed.$2",
    "Event.Forest_3": "With time, the our water source dried up. People started moving out, because farming wasn't possible anymore...$2#$b#I stayed. I didn't want to leave my students behind, but their families needed to. And it was for their sake, too.#$b#When I moved to the city, I lost contact. It was hard to find a new job, and it all began to pile up.#$b#Then, I heard of the valley.$7",
    "Event.Forest_4": "When i arrived, i didn't have where to stay...but by some coincidence, i met Gus. He offered a spare room i could stay at- in exchange of working there.#$b#He said, many people had the same experience as i did.",
    "Event.Forest_5":"Anyways, thanks for hearing my story.",
    "Event.Forest_question":"Why did you move here, @?",
    "Event.Forest_a1": "I wanted to escape the city, too.",
    "Event.Forest_a2": "It was my grandfather's farm.",
    "Event.Forest_a3": "I wanted money.",
    "Event.Forest_s1": "I see. So it's true...it's as if this place appears when you most need it.$7",
    "Event.Forest_s2": "So, he left it to you? Makes sense.",
    "Event.Forest_s3": "Really? That's it? $6#$b#You could make much more money at the city.",
    "Event.Forest_end": "Bueno, gracias por escucharme.",

    //  event: Saloon
    "Event.Saloon.base1": "...Yeah, and that's what we did.",
    "Event.Saloon.base2": "You seem a bit too amused...that crab almost tore my hair off.$2#$b#Though, you didn't escape their claws either.$1",
    "Event.Saloon.base3": "It's a bit hot...i'll go outside for a bit.",
    "Event.Saloon.baseChoice":"@, do you want to come with me?#I'll go with you.#I'll stay with Elliott.",

    "Event.Saloon.A-1":"Hey, @.#$e#I wanted to tell you something.#$e#You know...the town where i grew wasnt always so lonely.$0#$b#We used to be a tight knit community. The farms made money selling their goods, and would sell them to many places in Ferngill.",
    "Event.Saloon.A-2": "It was normal to see trains there. Sometimes, while i'd work at the school, i'd hear its whistle as it passed by.$0#$b#...Truth be told, i miss being teacher.$2#$b#I wonder if those kids, and their families, found a better place...$7",
    "Event.Saloon.A-3": "Sitting to watch for trains calmed me down. It reminded me of home. I had no idea if i'd fit here, and i was scared­.$2#$b#But, @... nowadays, i feel i'm part of the community.$7#$b#You've been a valuable friend to me­.$1#$b#I loved the town i grew in, and i'll miss it... but it's okay to move on, too. This is my home now.",
    "Event.Saloon.A-4":"...Elliot must be getting bored. We should head back.#$e#Hey, do you want a drink?$6#$b#My treat.$1",
    "Event.Saloon.A-end":"...#$b#I really appreciate you, @.$1",

    "Event.Saloon.B-1": "Sure.#$b#I won't take too long.$1",
    "Event.Saloon.B-2": "I get the feeling we'll have a while to talk.#$e#...@?$1#$b#Lately, i've noticed something quite intriguing.",
    "Event.Saloon.B-3":"...At first, Devan didn't talk much with our neighbors.#$b#They seemed...off, to be honest. Quite too distant.$2#$e#Except when Leah is around. Then, Devan loosens up a bit.",
    "Event.Saloon.B-4": "However...",
    "Event.Saloon.B-5": "Ever since you two became friends, Devan seems happier.#$b#You've made Devan feel at home here.",
    "Event.Saloon.B-6": "It's quite refreshing.$1",
    "Event.Saloon.B-7": "Hey, the breeze outside is very refreshing.#$b#Did i take too long?#$e#...Hey, what's with that face?$6",
    "Event.Saloon.B-end":"Not much. We were making small talk while waiting.#$b#I'd like to continue telling @ about when we tried the crab pots by ourselves.",
    
